meta.about: I love Ocean n do my best to bring ppl to stop the pollution from Selfish Human behaviour. To remove abandoned fishing nets , planting mangrove trees, picking up trash and self-physical and mental training through sports. To protect environment by action

meta.name: kittiGreenWorld
meta.about:
熱愛大自然、愛從事水上活動！
自發保育行動由10+年前，從潛水、游泳、行山、放假、划kayak也離不開執垃圾……
海洋拾荒者kitti 的夢……要感染更加多人加入成為戰友去面對自己每天製造的垃圾！打一場不易赢的仗……
